  "uuid": "3c2ae5c46b4f0de440107528d020f5f6",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Storeman / Yard Personnel",
  "description": "<p><u>Job Responsibilities:</u></p><ul><li>Full time station in store / yard and responsible for handling of daily operations</li><li>Receiving, inspecting, and storing incoming deliveries</li><li>Track and manage day to day delivery schedule, inclusive of receiving/issuing Delivery Order (DO) documents</li><li>Managing inventory and assisting in stock take (monthly / annually) physically.</li><li>Assist in tagging on steel material (RFID tag)</li><li>Maintain cleanliness / good housekeeping in store</li><li>Proper filing of stock in/out documentation and data entry</li><li>Able to compromise with construction timing, assist the operation site with all matters pertaining to the store / yard.</li><li>Report to Operation Manager</li><li>Any other ad-hoc duties when required</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><u>Job Requirements:</u></p><ul><li>Welcome entry level. Training will be provided. Would be beneficial if have experience in construction stores/ warehouse / logistics operations</li><li>Preferably with Forklift License</li><li>Minimum GCE “N”/”O” level</li><li>Basic knowledge in MS Office - Word & Excel, for updating inventory into the system</li><li>Meticulous, organized and able to work in fast-paced environment.</li><li>Able to work independently, a good team player with initiative and able to work with minimum supervision.</li><li>Able to handle heavy loads</li><li>Willing to work overtime as and when there is night shipment (up to 10pm)</li><li>Able to accept working in Tuas area</li><li>Proficiency in English and Chinese Language is preferred. </li><li>Able to start work immediately / within short notice</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><u>Others:</u></p><ul><li>6 days work week, 9am to 6pm</li><li>Overtime payment is given when been tasked</li><li>AWS upon confirmation and pro-rated if service is less than a year.</li><li>Performance Bonus subjected to individual and company’s performance.</li></ul>",
